{"tid":1796057,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英女王聖誕文告將罕有稱2019年崎嶇 約翰遜避談脫歐､籲少紛爭","createTime":"2019-12-24T10:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T16:15:46.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e59c945ef93a06f5099240286f531a2fa7ab15","tid":1796057,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2527277/25cafp002__1024_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2527277%2F25cafp002__1024_1024.jpg&h=d6b09609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英女王伊利沙伯二世將在聖誕文告中，罕有地以較負面的詞語形容2019年，稱是「崎嶇」（bumpy）的一年。首相約翰遜（Boris Johnson）發表聖誕講話，試圖避免使用「脫歐」字眼，呼籲民眾在聖誕期間不要有太多爭執。<br />\n<br />\n英國皇室發放了英女王聖誕文告的內容，被視為對脫歐困局及自己家庭的反思。文告影片將在英國時間明天（25日）下午3時全球播放，英女王將談及耶穌的一生及和解的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n四代同堂過聖誕 英女王與喬治王子焗布甸<br />\n<br />\n2016年的脫歐公投造成國家分裂，英女王呼籲國民克服彼此的分歧，營造和諧的氣氛和諒解。她說︰<br />\n<br />\n以信心和希望採取的小行動，有助克服長期以來、根深蒂固的分歧，從而帶來和諧與諒解&hellip;&hellip;當然，道路不總是一帆風順，今年也許有時會有些崎嶇，但小小的行動可帶來很大的改變。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2527277/25cafp003__1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2527277%2F25cafp003__1024_600.jpg&h=a59b9669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 約翰遜發表聖誕講話影片，感謝國民保健服務的醫護人員、警員及公務員在聖誕期間緊守崗位。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜發表聖誕講話影片，感謝國民保健服務（NHS）的醫護人員、警員及公務員在聖誕期間緊守崗位；希望民眾在未來的幾天過得愉快，敦促他們不要與任何人作出過多的爭論。<br />\n<br />\n約翰遜一直揚言，帶領英國如期在下月31日脫歐。他以呼籲國民反思這一年作結，並慶祝即將到來的美好。<br />\n<br />\n在野工黨黨魁郝爾彬（Jeremy Corbyn）料最後一次以黨魁身份發表聖誕講話，回應剛過去的大選，承認2019年是「艱難」的一年；工黨經歷了重大的選舉失利，未能成功推進改革，但聖誕節是傾聽、反思和記住教訓的機會。"},{"pid":"c3657db1bce5411d769045c11946dafa3d44d5d0","tid":1796057,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:57:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2525000/2527277/25cafp004__1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2525000%2F2527277%2F25cafp004__1024_600.jpg&h=44b59c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者：鄧燕君<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2527277/英女王聖誕文告將罕有稱2019年崎嶇%20約翰遜避談脫歐､籲少紛爭\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2527277%2F%E8%8B%B1%E5%A5%B3%E7%8E%8B%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%96%87%E5%91%8A%E5%B0%87%E7%BD%95%E6%9C%89%E7%A8%B12019%E5%B9%B4%E5%B4%8E%E5%B6%87%2520%E7%B4%84%E7%BF%B0%E9%81%9C%E9%81%BF%E8%AB%87%E8%84%AB%E6%AD%90%EF%BD%A4%E7%B1%B2%E5%B0%91%E7%B4%9B%E7%88%AD&d=nB3K3ojK8rN8kNU4dsXAYxx0icFY2nnrImD0qQ%2FuO9w%3D&h=5b1f726f\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2527277/英女王聖誕文告將罕有稱2019年崎嶇%20約翰遜避談脫歐､籲少紛爭</a>"},{"pid":"313789664547b52fd1152dd88a33fa4cc4c49535","tid":1796057,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T10:58:14.000Z","msg":"邊個唔想做港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;無憂無慮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939cf8ebcbb6a8239ed979bbe947c388097a9652","tid":1796057,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:46:20.000Z","msg":"事頭婆"},{"pid":"65e4155b2a16e02cc8da8ab6904ca4b8f6f24964","tid":1796057,"uid":245292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:47:49.000Z","msg":"事頭婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b32a36fee179fd2d98cdb7435308a82d450db0","tid":1796057,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T15:51:45.000Z","msg":"God save the Queen<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022c4472469c1b645ffbfcabf98ef7b4be21b923","tid":1796057,"uid":235025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"965c81d18c171a66b9328